{% About
   title="About Me"
   subtitle="I'm Ahad, the artist behind Ahad Animates. I specialize in creating high-quality 3D advertisements, product visualizations, and animations that help brands showcase their products with realism, creativity, and impact."
   content="<br/><br/><span class=\"text-neutral-400\">I believe every product has a story worth telling. By combining artistic creativity with technical precision, I create visuals that capture attention and leave a lasting impression. Whether it's a cinematic product advertisement, a detailed visualization, or a smooth animation, my goal is to deliver work that not only looks exceptional but also helps businesses connect with their audience and elevate their brand.</span>"
